{"tid":402884,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得對友情嘅執著真係不亞於愛情","createTime":"2017-09-16T17:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T10:43:27.000Z","uid":123663,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"15aff21a07b14589313c45ab5e0ed64d24e18041","tid":402884,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:46:26.000Z","msg":"我個人本身好易呷醋同易嬲，但好易比friend氹得番。我都自問有正常數量嘅朋友，始終有幾個係特別friend都有男有女。我係好愛friend嘅人，我可以為佢地做好多野，我唔中意同佢地鬧交，就算發下脾氣之後我都會即刻話：算啦我唔想鬧交傷到感情 之類嘅說話。<br />\n想問大家當你地同一個frd對大家嘅感情落差太大，即係你好愛佢 默默付出左好多 好光明正大咁付出好多嘅時候，但對方對你麻麻到有時比hard feeling你，係咪應該要放棄對方？<br />\n因為我真係好辛苦去維持一段關係which is一個我好中意好中意嚟friend嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想放手 我驚太chur但我又唔捨得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf4075c0bbd74d0b1ca2f1f6802a7fa3630d761","tid":402884,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:48:05.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"767c28e46c89e9bb852ffc1c891cbd885e8e69f7","tid":402884,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:48:16.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1a3347b0fece2a65744db352f9114edf66f0d015","tid":402884,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:48:30.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"280febcbe3594692f9de45095874226038a07a6d","tid":402884,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"389528fd147e95437a127873d32675ea95820ecc","tid":402884,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:48:50.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"b46ad3fc188c647a0bbc32b29a67e25f178e